ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: The course helped us improve speaking English. I would recommend this course.
Good for an international student who needs to improve english

It is a necessary course for student whose native language is not English, because he or she will have a lot of chances to speak and discuss with others in English in an easy manner, as well as refinement on his or her presentation.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Not bad. Since I do not like speaking english a lot, looks like this course does not a lot.
It helps and tells me how to gradually master English
